=== INSTALLING ===
You can install it by double clicking the 'MonoTouchStubProject.vsix' file in the build folder.

YOU WILL NEED TO COPY ALL THE MONOTOUCH DLLS FROM A MONOTOUCH INSTALLATION TO YOUR WINDOWS PC.  ALSO IT WILL REPORT REFERENCES NOT FOUND IF YOU DONT ADD THE APPROPRIATE LOCATION TO YOUR PROJECT CONFIGURATION.

If it breaks for some reason, then start an empty Visual Studio and go to 'Tools' => 'Extension Manager' where you can disable or remove it.

